EXPLANATION
BY THE LEGISLATIVE COUNCIL
OF
A N A C T
RELATING TO EDUCATION -- CERTIFICATION OF TEACHERS
***
1 This act would eliminate any requirement that any person who is employed as a physical
2 education teacher not be required to have a certification in adaptive physical education, unless they
3 were hired after July 1, 2025.
4 This act would take effect upon passage.
